icate output mapping for env var %q targeting step %q\"\n```\n\n**Parse Errors** (from parser.go):\n```go\n\"line %d col %d: expected %v, got %v\"\n\"duplicate workflow name %q\"\n\"step %q has multiple of 'prompt', 'run', 'workflow_name'\"\n\"step %q has none of 'prompt', 'run', or 'workflow_name'\"\n\"workflow %q has both \\\"host\\\" and \\\"container\\\" blocks\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### **9. CLI Command Structure & Help**\n\n**Help Text Storage:**\n- All help in `/cmd/cloche/help.go`, `subcommandHelp` map\n- One entry per command: init, health, run, status, logs, poll, list, stop, delete, tasks, loop, get, set, workflow, project, shutdown\n- Format: Structured text with Usage, Flags, Examples, Environment sections\n\n**Command Categories:**\n\n**Non-daemon (local):**\n- `init` - Bootstrap project\n- `health` - Query daemon HTTP API for health\n- `get`/`set` - Read/write run context\n- `tasks` - Query task pipeline\n- `workflow` - List/visualize workflows\n- `project` - Show project info\n\n**Daemon-dependent (require gRPC):**\n- `run` - Launch workflow\n- `status` - Query run state\n- `logs` - Stream/display logs\n- `poll` - Wait for runs\n- `list` - List all runs\n- `stop` - Cancel run\n- `delete` - Remove container\n- `loop` - Control orchestration\n- `shutdown` - Stop daemon\n\n---\n\n### **10. Interfaces & Hexagonal Architecture** (internal/ports/)\n\n**Store Interface** (ports/store.go):\n- `RunStore` - Create/get/update/list runs\n- `CaptureStore` - Save/get step executions\n- `LogStore` - Persist log files\n- `EvolutionStore` - Track workflow evolution\n\n**Container Runtime Interface** (ports/container.go):\n- `ContainerRuntime` - Start/stop/inspect/copy Docker containers\n- `ImageEnsurer` - (optional) Validate/rebuild images\n\n**Agent Adapter Interface** (ports/agent.go):\n- `AgentAdapter` - Execute agent steps in container\n\n---\n\n### **11. Version Strategy**\n\n**File:** `/workspace/internal/version/VERSION` (single line, currently \"1.3.0\")\n\n**Forma